Dourado EM</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2011-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>1422-0067</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>doi_53d087087d7939c1</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>800A9E3F-56A6-4A86-8B29-54DC67FC93D9</gtr:id><gtr:title>Computer simulation of volatile organic compound adsorption in atomistic models of molecularly imprinted polymers.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Langmuir : the ACS journal of surfaces and colloids</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/3144a3a5e72a50ce8f6172397c0f2b25"><gtr:id>3144a3a5e72a50ce8f6172397c0f2b25</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Herdes C</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2009-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0743-7463</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>doi_53d01a01ac3e7279</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>8078646A-23E5-4F10-9D68-2B56E9AE78B6</gtr:id><gtr:title>Integral Equation Theory of Adsorption in Templated Materials: Influence of Molecular Attraction</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>The Journal of Physical Chemistry C</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/1158682a09064ba499563f01c8c73913"><gtr:id>1158682a09064ba499563f01c8c73913</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Sarkisov L</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2007-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>doi_53d018018cd6b159</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>96DF712D-E3BC-4032-BB75-F46DD115FBCE</gtr:id><gtr:title>Emergence of molecular recognition phenomena in a simple model of imprinted porous materials.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>The Journal of chemical physics</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/2d63c3982ec0a5ec0ff8eb6e538c1422"><gtr:id>2d63c3982ec0a5ec0ff8eb6e538c1422</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Dourado EM</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2009-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0021-9606</gtr:issn><gtr:outcomeId>doi